n17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012379, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Moallif say that the son of Sayed Ibne Tawoos has recorded this ziyarat in Zawaaedul Fawaaed and said this ziyarat of Lady Fatema (s) is to be recited on the day of her shahadat which is on 3rd Jamadi-us-Saani, he say that before ziyarat recite 2 rakat namaz-e-ziyarat of Lady Fatema (s), in each rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 60 times and if you can’t do that then in 1st rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> once and in 2nd rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Kaafiroon> once. After namaz recite the following ziyarat…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Moallif kehte hai keh Sayed Ibne Tawoos ke farzand ne bhi is ziyarat ko Zawaaedul Fawaaed mein darj kiya aur kaha hai; yeh ziyarat Janabe Zahra (s) ke yaum-e-shahadat ke liye khaas hai jo 3rd Jamadi-us-Saani ko huwi thi, unho ne aap ki ziyarat ki kaifiyat is tarah bayaan ki hai keh 2 rakat Namaz-e-Ziyarat Bibi Fatema (s) padhe aur uski har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 60 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe, agar is qadr na padh sakey to phir 1st rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad ek martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> aur 2nd rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad ek martaba <Surah Kaafiroon> padhe aur namaz ke baad is tarah se ziyarat padhe…", "UrduDescription": "مؤلف کہتے ہیں : سید ابن طاؤسؒ کے فرزند نے بھی اس زیارت کو زوائدالفوائد میں درج کیا اور کہا ہے : یہ زیارت جناب زہرا ؑکے یوم ِرحلت کے لئے خاص ہے جو تیسری جمادی الثانی کو ہوئی تھی انہوں نے آپ کی زیارت کی کیفیت اس طرح بیان کی ہے کہ ۲ رکعت نماز زیارت بجا لائے یا نماز جناب سیدہ فاطمۃالزہرا (س)پڑھے جو ۲ رکعت ہے اور اس کی ہر رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۶۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے اگر اس قدر نہ پڑھ سکے تو پھر پہلی رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ایک مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> اور دوسری رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ایک مرتبہ <سورۂ کافرون> پڑھے اور نماز کے بعد مذکورہ بالا زیارت پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010576, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon you, O doyenne of the women of the world! Peace be upon you, O mother of the Arguments on all people! Peace be upon you, O wronged one whose right was usurped. O Allah, send blessings to Your lady servant, the daughter of Your Prophet, the wife of the Successor of Your Prophet, such remarkable blessings that approach her nearer to You than the steps of Your honored servants among the inhabitants of the heavens and the earth.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho aap par ay jahano ki aurto’n ki sardaar. Salaam ho aap par ay unki waaleda jo logo’n par Khuda ki hujjate’n hai. Salaam ho aap par ay woh mazlooma jis ka haq chheen liya gaya. Ay Ma’bood! Rehmat naazil farma apni kaneez, apne Nabi ki dukhtar aur apne Nabi ke Wasi ki sharike hayaat par aisi rehmat jo nazdik kare usko badh kar Teri izzat waale bando’n ki nisbat jo aasmaano mein rehne waale aur zameen mein basne waale hai.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو آپ ؑپر اے جہانوں کی عورتوں کی سردار سلام ہو آپ ؑپر اے ان کی والدہ جو لوگوں پر خدا کی حجتیں ہیں سلام ہو آپ ؑپر اے وہ مظلومہ جس کا حق چھین لیا گیا۔ اے معبود! رحمت نازل فرما اپنی کنیز اپنے نبیؐ کی دختر اور اپنے نبیؐ کے وصی ؑکی شریکۂ حیات پر ایسی رحمت جو نزدیک کرے اس کو بڑھ کر تیری عزّت والے بندوں کی نسبت جو آسمانوں میں رہنے والے اور زمین میں بسنے والے ہیں۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE YAA SAYYEDA-TA NESAAA-IL AA’LAMEENA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE YAA WAALEDA-TIL HOJA-JE A’LAN NAASE AJMA-EE’NA. AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKE AYYA-TO-HAL MAZLOOMA-TUL MAMNOO-A’TO HAQQA-HAA. ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA AMATE-KA WABNA-TE NABIYYEKA WA ZAWJA-TE WASIYYE NABIYYE-KA SALAA-TAN TUZLE-FOHAA FAWQA ZULFAA E’BAADE-KAL MOKARRA-MEENA MIN AHLIS SAMAA-WAATE WA AHLIL ARA-ZEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ يَا سَيِّدَةَ نِسَآءِ الْعَالَمِيْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ يَا وَالِدَةَ الْحُجَجِ عَلَى النَّاسِ اَجْمَعِينَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَيْكِ اَيَّتُهَا الْمَظْلُوْمَةُ الْمَمْنُوْعَةُ حَقَّهَا۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى اَمَتِكَ وَابْنَةِ نَبِيِّكَ وَزَوْجَةِ وَصِيِّ نَبِيِّكَ صَلَاةً تُزْلِفُهَا فَوْقَ زُلْفٰى عِبَادِكَ الْمُكَرَّمِيْنَ مِنْ اَهْلِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَاَهْلِ الْاَرَضِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlu